task.summary: Initial cut at checking that delegator passes a block correctly.
Added test support for delegation with arguments and blocks
Added check to ensure correct block was passed.
Added additional specs for delegating to instance variables.
Added support to specify different args to be received by delegate.
Improved failure messages with blocks and arguments.
Updated xxx_ok? and xxx_failure_message logic to be more similar.
Improved failure message with allow_nil option.
Simplified descriptions when delegate method or name is the same as the delegator.
Simplified failure messages to only use super if delegation did not happen at all
Initial cut at delegating to an object
Minor refactoring for delegating to objects
Added support for incorrect return value from delegator.
Ensure nil is return when allow_nil is true
Split Pad::Configuration into its own file and added specs for it.
Added ability to set delegate method via ".as(xxx)" and removed ability to specify delegate method via ".to(xxx)"
Updated pad to use more capabilities of the delegate matcher
Cleaned up specs to test behaviour.
Added entity specs (typo as model was listed twice)
